cfa7b2d3-a28e-40a7-8ccf-cc3db334fa5e.text: Leon is gazing intently at the crossbow in his hands.

options.text: What is this place?
Can you tell me about your crossbow?
Tell me about the ammo for your crossbow.
I'll be off now, excuse me.

f3b78d59-5229-4844-8430-fa38e78d14f8.title: Leon
f3b78d59-5229-4844-8430-fa38e78d14f8.text:
This is Aleck's Hunter Emporium. Basically, it's just a
shop with a fancy name; you can buy various weapons
and traps here.

options.text: Can I buy some equipment from the shop then?
Can you tell me about your crossbow?
Tell me about the ammo for your crossbow.
I'll be off now, excuse me.

2a489f47-bc39-40d6-b779-24feb2dff73b.title: <player>
2a489f47-bc39-40d6-b779-24feb2dff73b.text: Can I buy some equipment from the shop then?

8ceb4381-d928-44f7-9cf1-66b407ba2131.title: Leon
8ceb4381-d928-44f7-9cf1-66b407ba2131.text:
Oh, this isn't my shop; the owner is Aleck over there
behind the counter.

b0fe517c-2fc8-466a-892d-9d58abc553f1.title: Leon
b0fe517c-2fc8-466a-892d-9d58abc553f1.text:
I experiment with weapon designs. I'm here because
I've been trying to convince people to back my research
and maybe sell some of my product - like this one I'm
holding - in their shops.

be79a01f-eba1-4b26-bcdc-5faaeb59210f.title: Leon
be79a01f-eba1-4b26-bcdc-5faaeb59210f.text: Aleck doesn't seem to be interested though.

options.text: Can you tell me about your crossbow?
Tell me about the ammo for your crossbow.
I'll be off now, excuse me.

9a5271ac-32b8-4d93-b6f6-f7a2f1a1bdf5.title: <player>
9a5271ac-32b8-4d93-b6f6-f7a2f1a1bdf5.text: Can you tell me about your crossbow?

f01aa907-8e49-4f5c-b35b-9b2b5ce04e9a.title: Leon
f01aa907-8e49-4f5c-b35b-9b2b5ce04e9a.text:
It's good isn't it? I designed it to incorporate the bones
of various animals in its construction.

52cb2d77-9aa9-4409-a4d0-4d07603ca573.title: Leon
52cb2d77-9aa9-4409-a4d0-4d07603ca573.text:
It's a fair bit faster than an ordinary crossbow too; it'll
take you far less time to reload between shots.

options.text: That's crazy, it'll never work!
That sounds good. Let's trade.
Tell me about the ammo for your crossbow.
I'll be off now, excuse me.

8143f853-433c-465b-a0fb-ddd610f926e2.title: Leon
8143f853-433c-465b-a0fb-ddd610f926e2.text:
That's what they said about my wind-powered mouse
traps, too.

d82ccdb1-af92-4020-bf4f-26ab04f5c80d.title: Leon
d82ccdb1-af92-4020-bf4f-26ab04f5c80d.text:
Well, they only ran into problems because people kept
insisting on trying to use them indoors.

768ba5e5-ed48-4467-9e74-db56a6ca69a9.title: Leon
768ba5e5-ed48-4467-9e74-db56a6ca69a9.text:
Anyway, I think my crossbow invention is showing a lot
more promise.

options.text: That sounds good. Let's trade.
Tell me about the ammo for your crossbow.
I'll be off now, excuse me.

6f4c5fb5-5f01-4a9b-9450-c3733d5f9a9d.title: <player>
6f4c5fb5-5f01-4a9b-9450-c3733d5f9a9d.text: Tell me about the ammo for your crossbow.

7e4a3db1-5cab-47c7-aa1e-bcb8079b32ff.title: Leon
7e4a3db1-5cab-47c7-aa1e-bcb8079b32ff.text:
Ah, I admit as a result of its... er... unique construction,
it won't take just any old bolts.

dd3c788c-f241-4e89-86ae-7b0dc8b5c4c5.title: Leon
dd3c788c-f241-4e89-86ae-7b0dc8b5c4c5.text:
If you can supply the materials and a token fee, I'd be
happy to make some for you.

fe9fe58b-254f-4d4a-b70a-e745867d2182.title: Leon
fe9fe58b-254f-4d4a-b70a-e745867d2182.text:
I need kebbit spikes, lots of  'em. Not all kebbits have
spikes mind you. You'll be wanting prickly kebbits or,
even better, razor-backed kebbits to get materials hard
enough.

options.text: Can't I just make my own?
Okay, can you make ammo for me?
Can you tell me about your crossbow?
I'll be off now, excuse me.

c8dc729c-9283-46a1-a3a7-0c470f3aa416.title: <player>
c8dc729c-9283-46a1-a3a7-0c470f3aa416.text: I'll be off now, excuse me.

88c6a6c8-57e7-44cd-a40e-d8fb470d35e5.title: Leon
88c6a6c8-57e7-44cd-a40e-d8fb470d35e5.text:
Well, if you ever find yourself in need of that
innovative edge, you can always find me here.

d257610c-bf43-4856-811e-8947ec128320.title: <player>
d257610c-bf43-4856-811e-8947ec128320.text: Can't I just make my own?

a682b2e6-7169-4ecd-8c2a-dc1e45a8004f.title: Leon
a682b2e6-7169-4ecd-8c2a-dc1e45a8004f.text:
Yes, I suppose you could, although you'll need a steady
hand with a knife and a chisel.

a880768d-2309-4b1e-b29c-5a1e4272857b.title: Leon
a880768d-2309-4b1e-b29c-5a1e4272857b.text:
The bolts have an unusual diameter, but basically you'll
just need to be able to carve kebbit spikes into straight
shafts.

21f01b0a-55a5-4c41-a44c-bfc37850057a.title: Leon
21f01b0a-55a5-4c41-a44c-bfc37850057a.text:
Meanwhile, since you're here, I can make some for you
if you have the materials.

options.text: Okay, can you make ammo for me?
Can you tell me about your crossbow?
I'll be off now, excuse me.
